OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunshine then a dry night with some
OL,7,Fclear periods, though perhaps cloudier
OL,8,Facross eastern Lanarkshire.
OL,9,
OL,10,CSaturday:FA good deal of dry weather
OL,11,Fwith the best of the sunshine towards
OL,12,Fthe west coast. Cloud building inland
OL,13,Fperhaps bringing the odd light shower.
OL,14,FA bit colder.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry with sunny spells on Sunday, some
OL,18,Flight rain in evening. Monday dry and
OL,19,Fbright, some showers west coast, then
OL,20,Fsome patchy evening rain. Sunny
OL,21,Fintervals and showers Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
